The paper deals with color constancy, which is a problem in computer vision and image processing. The use of derivative colors and kernel density estimation suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) or graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. The paper also involves modeling and estimation, which could place it in the multimedia (cs.MM), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), or machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
